&lt;p>4.得到直播推流地址：&lt;/p>
&lt;p>&lt;img src="https://blog.tuwei.space/p/kplayer-24%E5%B0%8F%E6%97%B6bilibili%E7%9B%B4%E6%92%AD%E6%8E%A8%E6%B5%81-docker%E9%83%A8%E7%BD%B2%E6%95%99%E7%A8%8B/img_4.png"
width="797"
